data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Leaf River, IL! This charming 2-story offers a perfect blend of modern updates and timeless elegance. With 4 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, and a host of desirable features, this property is sure to capture your heart. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of original hardwood floors and stunning woodwork that adds character and charm to every room. The spacious living area is perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing with your loved ones. The updated kitchen boasts sleek countertops and ample cabinet space. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find a convenient dining area where you can enjoy family meals and create lasting memories. Upstairs, you'll find four cozy bedrooms, providing plenty of space for the whole family to unwind and recharge. The master bedroom features large windows that fill the room with natural light, creating a peaceful retreat to escape the hustle and bustle of daily life. Outside, the back porch offers the perfect spot to soak in the unobstructed views of the surrounding landscape and enjoy beautiful sunsets in the evening. Additional highlights of this home include a new roof installed in 2023, as well as newer furnace and siding, heated 2.5 garage, 15’ pool and  providing peace of mind for years to come. Don't miss your chance to make this exquisite home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of comfortable living in Leaf River, IL!
